reviewText: How can we forget Milli Vanelli? Despite all the controversy, these guys really finished the 80's in style, their hit song "Girl I'm Gonna Miss You" was in heavy rotation in 1989, and what a hit it was, if you want to revisit the era of real music, this tape is the one to buy.
The video is in excellent condition. The sound track is great n so is the cover. I am enjoying the video very much
great if you want to relive the days gone by. i grew up on this. despite the controversy. i love this

The videos are : blame it on the rain, baby don't forget my number, girl you know is true,girl i'm gonna miss you, no more, and the sound is not excellente is aceptable....don't forget is a vhs,  i wanna like all the video but worse nothing..
If you like Milli Vanilli, this tape is essential viewing.  The songs are great and the videos are, well, the fun you would expect from pop meisters MV.  Shout out to Rob and Fav!!
